# 🎮 Leloxencia: City Life Saga

**Leloxencia: City Life say whattt** is a dreamy 3D adventure game starring *you* and *your bestie*! 💑✨  
Live your best aesthetic life — explore, survive, and thrive together in a vibey city full of love, tech, and fun.

## 🌟 Features

- 🧍‍♀️ **Custom 3D Models**: You and besie brought to life in-game!
- 🏠 **Home Sweet Home**: A cozy shared house with interior detail and homely feels.
- 🚗 **Drive Around Town**: Hop into your BMW and cruise through a vibrant city filled with malls, clubs, and parks.
- ⏰ **Dynamic Day/Night Cycles**: Beautiful transitions from morning to night — aesthetic and real-time.
- 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 **Interactive Town**: Explore areas with people, universities, schools, and other families' homes.
- 🎓 **Presidents of IT**: You and Dylan are top of the digital world in your own university!
- 💎 **33 Fun Levels**: Progress through interactive challenges, earning coins and bonuses.
- 🏆 **Final Reward**: At Level 33, unlock **100,000 coins** and a **golden trophy**.
- 🛠️ **Web-Based & Responsive**: Built with Three.js and HTML/CSS, it works on all modern browsers and devices.
- 🚧 **Version 2 Coming Soon...**

## 📁 Project Structure

```bash
📦 LeloxenciaGame/
├── assets/
│   ├── models/           # 3D models (characters, house, car)
│   ├── sounds/           # Sound effects and ambient music
├── scripts/
│   ├── movement.js       # Walking, driving, interaction logic
│   ├── timeSystem.js     # Morning, afternoon, night logic
├── index.html            # Game entry point
├── style.css             # Aesthetic styling
├── main.js               # Main game logic & scene setup
└── README.md             # This file 💖
